<sup>1</sup>Some states recognize marriages performed elsewhere, other states such as New Jersey actually encourage it, especially when the spouses were not residents of the state when married.{{sup|[[WP:Please clarify|clarification needed<!-- needs clarification regarding the [[Full Faith and Credit Clause]] of the U.S. constitution -->]]}}]]

[[Cousin marriage]] acceptance differs from one [[U.S. state]] to another ranging from being legal to a criminal offense.

